metadata.name: OSIRIS NFT.NYC 2022
metadata.description:
**OSIRIS NFT.NYC 2022  Special Edition** dedicated to THE 4TH ANNUAL NFT INDUSTRY EVENT JUNE 20-23, 2022.

**OSIRIS NFT.NYC 2022  Special Edition** consist of 22 pcs:

- 1st piece and 1 of 1 **OSIRIS NFT.NYC 2022** version listed on FND as first produced and has Serial Number #01. 

- 21 other versions will be released on official **UASIS CORP** [website](https://osirisone.uasiscorp.com) at June 25.
